            <abstract id="ref9" label="Abstract">Swiss fair exhibition on women in Zurich,
                Switzerland, that was built by Swiss women architects. Collection consists of
                sixty-three drawings of the buildings, including the collaborative work of Claire
                Rufer-Eckmann, Beate Billeter, Verena Fuhrimann, Jetti Judin-Mutzenberg, and
                Annemarie Hubacher-Constam.</abstract>                 
